    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/bd4e8ec211c1764136ad966541ae3864.avif?t=1745599808\" width=616 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/b3b3ad628d24624a99cf34dc712b7cfd.webp?t=1745599808\" width=616 height=50 /></span>Dire Fog combines the best strategic elements of turn based tactical combat and deck building card games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct your deck and then play it out on a grid, strategically maneuvering your minions and spells into position to outwit your opponent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/6a1f26714c21c3c5ce38d7496533dd45.avif?t=1745599808\" width=610 height=186 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/30b709db4302feaf7d43f89754f65230.webp?t=1745599808\" width=616 height=50 /></span>Choose the order your cards are drawn in when you build your deck. There are no random effects in the game and no shuffling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can only win through thoughtful deck construction and outplaying your opponent in game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/bcbfd2c91cdc69bbd5aff575d3937165.webp?t=1745599808\" width=616 height=50 /></span>Dire Fog is designed to be first and foremost a strategic PVP experience. You will build a deck and play it against an opponent selected based on your skill level online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/5c813ddcda0d53544bb1f4ec50c3ea9d.avif?t=1745599808\" width=616 height=176 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unique effects that play into positioning mechanics and offer opportunities to set up and outplay your opponent</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Stunning visual effects, hand drawn illustrations, and voice overs that will leave you breathless</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Lore and world building baked into every card that will draw you in to the world of Dire Fog</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/ef2f00bf750d997006c7240154a9e7d1.webp?t=1745599808\" width=616 height=50 /></span>Dire Fog is currently in the closed alpha stage of development. We are welcome dedicated fans of CCGs and deep tactical combat games to join our community and provide their feedback and thoughts!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our discord server!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
